{"tid":881250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[歐洲動態] 默克爾準備下台？","createTime":"2018-10-29T09:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T14:26:18.000Z","uid":141151,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8609698b902495d87a7c974fd0c5420ceba92c2b","tid":881250,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:46:38.000Z","msg":"FB: 歐洲動態<br />\n<br />\n默克爾準備下台？<br />\n<br />\n多間德國傳媒引述消息人士報導，德國總理默克爾已向黨內人士表示，無意在今年12月黨大會上尋求連任CDU黨魁，結束超過18年的黨魁領導。<br />\n<br />\n現在需要關注，這是否意味默克爾將在年底至明年初卸任總理一職。她之前一向表示，總理應由黨魁兼任。<br />\n<br />\n繼姊妹黨CSU兩週前在地選慘敗後，CDU在星期日的黑森州地選得票率急挫10個百分點。<br />\n<br />\nAngela Merkel will not run for CDU party chair again - party sources<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dw.com/en/angela-merkel-will-not-run-for-cdu-party-chair-again-party-sources/a-46068450?fbclid=IwAR2-X1LbFMHv4u-PK3zV3STzPQfWkY28gsd-uCO-RqSoIDE9H_M3yFXCZRI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fangela-merkel-will-not-run-for-cdu-party-chair-again-party-sources%2Fa-46068450%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2-X1LbFMHv4u-PK3zV3STzPQfWkY28gsd-uCO-RqSoIDE9H_M3yFXCZRI&d=KTBDpI4eu99qGD55MLZpZm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=17af77ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dw.com/en/angela-merkel-will-not-run-for-cdu-party-chair-again-party-sources/a-46068450?fbclid=IwAR2-X1LbFMHv4u-PK3zV3STzPQfWkY28gsd-uCO-RqSoIDE9H_M3yFXCZRI</a>"},{"pid":"5ea69767e9585117f4ab1385d103150e6fd380a8","tid":881250,"uid":2772,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:48:01.000Z","msg":"引入難民問題就拍拍蘿友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906000ced422b1b7400e8aebae012c958d1e7722","tid":881250,"uid":70786,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T09:59:22.000Z","msg":"仆街死啦死肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126d134e5335a90b1d2e88d321e58a509409b652","tid":881250,"uid":26601,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T10:11